704209f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Lefferts Avenue
704209f-a.text:
502 Flatbush Ave., west side, opposite Lefferts Ave., showing a two
story frame house possibly belonging at one time to one Neefus. In the
realty Atlas of Brooklyn (1929) there is a three story structure on the
site, of either stone or stucco.
About 1920.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
